These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, water, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, italian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the thai is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the italian is not the person drinking tea##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the thai##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
7. the brazilian is somewhere between the person drinking water and the colombian##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking water##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water   | milk      | fanta   | tea  |
| Nationality   | thai    | italian   | brazilian | colombian  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

