3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the boat is not the person drinking tea##6
5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the snowmobile##7
8. the person driving the scooter is not the person drinking milk##6
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
