The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cricket, parkour, sailing
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
4. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
5. the fan of punk is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is sailing##7
8. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
9. the fan of blues is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is cricket##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | punk    | blues    | metal     |
| Color   | ivory | light-blue | lilac  | blood-red |
| Sport         | sailing    | parkour | baseball | cricket   |

